                                                        <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                            <div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
                                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ABA-Resources is a professional training hub for professionals and parents who interact with, teach, care for, and treat individuals with autism spectrum disorder (ASD and other developmental disorders ). ABA Resources was developed by a team of professionals and Parents; with over 15 years of experience in the field. This dynamic team has worked together to create and implement diversity training and development programs. Our innovative course offerings meet the current and emerging needs of the community, parents, caregivers, and professionals across the globe in general and are specially designed for the Arabic community.</span></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ABA Resources team shares a passion for working with kids with developmental delays and their families. Our journey working with professionals, kids, and families taught us how important it is to have access to the information they need to understand and be active in their child’s therapy. We also learned about the many barriers that get in the way of accessing quality evidence-based therapy, including high costs, limited numbers of therapists, and insufficient information and training, and most importantly unavailability of training in Arabic.</span></p>					</div>
